    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to believe it's all just about 'trust' when the timing is so surgical. the second i started asking questions about where the compliance funds were actually going, the invitations started. and now they've even suggested i relocate to the new satellite office to 'lead a special task force'. it feels less like a career boost and more like they're trying to isolate me from my old team so i can't talk to anyone about what i found. don't you think that looks a bit like they're trying to contain me?",
